title: Bonus Episode w/ Guests Jim Jones and Tracy Morgan
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 1/13/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez, and the crew are in the studio with Tracy Morgan talking about Eddie Murphy and Coming to America 2, his friend Betty White, and much more! Jim Jones talks NFT's, saving lives, Lobby Boyz, and much more!
